                "title": "Book Reader Activity Badge",
                "image": "../../images/badges/cu-as-bore.png",
                "description": "<div id=\"body_text\"><h2>Book Reader Activity Badge </h2><img src='../../images/badges/cu-as-bore.png' alt='Book Reader Activity Badge ' title='Book Reader Activity Badge ' height='150' width='150' align='right' style='margin-left:10px;'><br><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">To gain this badge, Cub Scouts must complete the following:</span><ol><li> <p>Makea list of at least six books read or used recently. Name their authorsand be able to tell the leader or other members of the Pack somethingabout three of the books. The three books chosen should include atleast one fiction and one non-fiction book.</p></li><li> <p>Understand and know how to care for your books.</p></li><li> <p>Show that you can use a dictionary, encyclopaedia and an atlas.</p></li><li> <p>Explain to a leader how the books in a library are set out and how you would find fiction and non-fiction books.<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span></p></li></ol></p><p>&nbsp;</p> </div>"
